1.title: Prison Cell
1.description: You wake up in a dark prison cell with a goblin guard sleeping right outside. You feel a bump on your head that brings back painful memories of getting hit by a rock.

2.title: Goblin Dungeon
2.description: You are in a dark corridor with several prison cells on your left and your right. A door lies ahead.

3.title: Goblin King Room
3.description: The room you are in appears to be decorated with the finest goblin jewels and tapestries. Directly in the back of the room there is a goblin-sized throne with skulls on it.  This must be the Goblin King's Throne Room.
